ganga/python/GangaLHCb
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ganga 6.0.11 (from GangaLHCb-24-51)
************

Further to core changes:

1) utilise named templates system to set up the 'templatesLHCb' registry of named templates which
will in time hold a collection of best practise templates or standard debugging templates for use
within the LHCb community.

2) made less verbose the error messages pronted out from the LHCb metadata methods e.g. lumi. It is
now the case that the trace back is no longer reported in favour of just the simple warning. (see
Savannah #101383).


